<br>
However, if you go up to an NPC wielding a weapon, and attempt to disarm it, you will ONLY AGRO IF SUCCESSFUL. Therefore, you can only generate hate on a mob holding a weapon that can be disarmed, and you will only generate hate on the round that you disarm.<br>
<br>
The same is true for beg. Begging won't always agro mobs, only if your failure is so dysmal that it pisses them off.  <p>Trindade<br>
